(27) ‘Schengen Information System’ or ‘SIS’ means the Scheng en Information System established by Regulations 
(EU) 2018/1860, (EU) 2018/1861 and (EU) 2018/1862;  
(28) ‘ECRIS- TCN’ means the centralised system for the identif ication of Member States holding conviction information 
